            clinical: "<b>Cryptorchidism:</b> Testis fails to descend → infertile + tumour-prone. <b>Cystic Endometrial Hyperplasia / Pyometra (Bitch):</b> Common, life-threatening. <b>Mammary Tumours (Bitch):</b> ~50% malignant. <b>Mastitis:</b> Bacterial inflammation of mammary alveoli.",
            imgCode: "reproductive_histo"
